title: Death Road to Canada v05.12.2017
description: Death Road to Canada is a Randomly Generated Road Trip Simulator. You control and manage a car full of jerks as they explore cities, recruit weird people, argue with each other, and face gigantic swarms of slow zombies.Death Road is built for replay value. Everything is randomized: locations, events, survivor appearances and personalities.
